  "time_ut": 1659439574,
  "original_lang": "ta",
  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bc0\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0b85\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0ba4\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0bc1\u0b9a\u0bcd \u0b9a\u0bc6\u0bb2\u0bcd\u0bb2\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f \u0bae\u0bc2\u0bb5\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0b8e\u0ba9\u0bcd\u0ba9 \u0ba8\u0b9f\u0ba8\u0bcd\u0ba4\u0ba4\u0bc1?",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "What happened to the drowned trio?",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The search for the three people who were swept away in the water yesterday at Navalapitti Ketabula-Akkarakanda Estate is still going on today.",
        "In Ketabula Akkarakanda river, which is a branch of the Mahavali river, when it rains, it is common for the water to go over the bridge and people cross the bridge with the help of a rope.",
        "At that time, 45-year-old Jayaletsumi, a mother of 3 children, who was engaged in gardening, slipped and fell into the river while trying to cross the bridge with the help of a rope.",
        "After this, 52-year-old Sathyaseelan, a father of 3, and 36-year-old Chandramohan, a father of 3, from Athottam, tried to save the woman, but they too were swept away.",
        "The soldiers of the Kothmalai military station have arrived today at 12 noon to search for them and the Navalapitti police and the general public are working together to search for the missing persons."
      ],
